    "There are a total of ten disease types found in tomatoes in this data set.",
    "Some diseases that may damage plants are target spots, septoria leaf spots, mosaic viruses, leaf molds, healthy spots, and bacterial spots.",
    "The research investigated four common transfer learning-based architectures: LeNet, Xception, ResNet50, and VGG16.",
    "Classification accuracies of 96.27%, 98.13%, 98.65%, and 99.25% were achieved by evaluating the efficacy of these Abiotic plant stress and biotic plant diseases.",
